frontmatter.title: Rishikesh Trip | Where It All Started!!!
frontmatter.description: Where it all started!!!. I think this is the best I can describe that journey. My first solo trip,  my first trip in fact. I had never traveled before just for the fun of it. Every place I had visited earlier was either for work or family obligations. This was my first trip for fun, for leisure, for me. My solo one day trip to Rishikesh
